RACE.FOOTNOTES: SPICYBUG was closest in pursuit from outside, bid two wide into the lane, dueled in the stretch and held a short lead over KISSED BY FIRE entering the final sixteenth, then drew clear in the end. KISSED BY FIRE sped to the front and showed the way up the backstretch, led along the rail through the turn, challenged by SPICYBUG entering the lane, dueled to the sixteenth pole and yielded late. NORTH EAST STAR (IRE) was off slow and lagged behind early, went outside a rival in the two path on the turn, angled four wide into the lane, moved out further in the stretch then drifted inward and was along for the show. IRRESISTIBLE FORCE broke a step slow, chased along the inside, tipped off the fence in the drive and lacked a bid. IRISH ROSE broke a step slow, sat off the pace, raced near the inside into the turn, two wide into the lane, moved out in the drive and improved position. TIFF WITH JIMMY tracked the pace from inside into and around the turn, remained along the fence in the lane and lacked a rally. DANCING MO was off a bit slow in the beginning, tracked three wide into the turn, raced outside a pair of rivals around the bend, got floated out a touch at the top of the stretch and also lacked a rally. MIZZTIFY DOLL chased in range early, rounded the bend two wide, moved out at the top of the stretch and weakened. CHROME DESSERT came away slow, traveled near the back in the early going, raced along the rail then two wide into the stretch and failed to make an impact.
